":"January 16, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Satan is a wolf amongst humanity like the wolf who seizes the sheep wandering and straying from the flock. Beware of the winding mountain paths. You must stay with the wider community.\u201d Source: Musnad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/01\/08\/salaf-moderation-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":22799,"position":2},"title":"Salaf on Moderation: Devil pleased with either extremism or leniency","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Dawud reported: Makhlad ibn al-Husyan, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAllah never recommends something to His servants but that Satan interferes with it in one of two ways. He does not care which of them succeeds. Either he makes them exaggerate in it, or he makes\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19870,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/09\/19\/umar-on-secrecy\/","url_meta":{"origin":22799,"position":3},"title":"Umar on II Secrecy: Beware secret religious cults of misguidance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Awza\u2019i reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you see people meeting in s